==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Half nelson
<hw>Half nelson</hw>. <fld>(Wrestling)</fld> <def>A hold in which one
arm is thrust under the corresponding arm of the opponent, generally
behind, and the hand placed upon the back of his neck. In the
<col><b>full nelson</b></col> both hands are so placed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Halfness</ent>⟦br⟧
